data.description: Welcome to Parkwood subdivision!  Back on the market at no fault of the seller.  This immaculate home has been loved and well taken care of, and it's ready for you to move in!  The three-bedroom, two-bathroom home sits on a corner lot that's almost half an acre in size and includes a grand entrance, a large great room with a fireplace, a formal dining room, a breakfast nook island, and many recent updates.  New items that have been added recently are fresh paint, a gas range, insulated windows, light fixtures, 2019 roof, and flooring in the kitchen & bathroom.  This beautiful home also features chair molding, an attached garage,  utility room, dual closets in the owners bedroom, solid surface countertops, a fenced-in backyard, and a 160-foot deck that is perfect for entertaining and relaxing. Island bar in the breakfast nook will convey with the sale.  It's located in the southern part of Florence, close to MUSC, McLeod Hospital, numerous restaurants, shops, schools, entertainment, and sports facilities.  Back on the market through no fault of the seller.  Talk to a Realtor right away to find out more and set up a tour!
